title: Denma
synopsis: Dike the Invincible Death is the #1 target for bounty hunters across planet Urano. After getting drugged by a mysterious woman in a bar, Dike wakes up in the body of Denma, a 12-year-old space courier. With Denma's powers as a Quanx, he journeys across the galaxy fighting futuristic societies, flying spaceships, and foiling insidious plots, all to get his body back.
author: YoungsoonYang
